name: Sun rise
description: Created by Denys Krupodorov aka Jungle Symbol. Website: https://www.junglesymbol.com.  They say a person who has cognized sexuality in themselves attains the state of enlightenment of a human being. Internal energy goes without a gender. Its tides, like a sunrise that illuminates everything around, break through the physical body with flaming whirlwinds of emotions that go from within the soul.
